Beguiling Aura									KEY:Beguiling Aura ~ Nereid					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Aura.Supernatural			DEFINE:NereidBeguilingAuraDC|0	DESC:Any creature sexually attracted to women runs the risk of being beguiled by a nereid if it looks upon her beauty from a distance of 30 feet or less.  If the creature fails a DC %1 Will save, it is immediately fascinated.  A nereid may use her suggestion spell-like ability at will against creatures that are fascinated by her beguiling aura.  This is a mind-affecting compulsion effect.|NereidBeguilingAuraDC																																		BONUS:VAR|NereidBeguilingAuraDC|10+TL/2+CHA	BONUS:VAR|NereidBeguilingAuraDC|2|PREFEAT:1,Ability Focus (Beguiling Aura)	SOURCEPAGE:p.198
Drowning Kiss									KEY:Drowning Kiss ~ Nereid					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural	DEFINE:NereidDrowningKissDC|0		DESC:A nereid can flood the lungs of a willing, helpless, or fascinated creature by touching it (traditionally by kissing the creature on the lips).  If the target cannot breathe water, it cannot hold its breath and immediately begins to drown.  On its turn, the target can attempt a DC %1 Fortitude save to cough up this water; otherwise it falls unconscious at 0 hp.  On the next round, the target must save again or drop to -1 hit points and be dying; on the third round it must save again or die (see page 445 of the Pathfinder RPG Core Rulebook).|NereidDrowningKissDC							BONUS:VAR|NereidDrowningKissDC|10+TL/2+CON	BONUS:VAR|NereidDrowningKissDC|2|PREFEAT:1,Ability Focus (Drowning Kiss)	SOURCEPAGE:p.198
